If you have Multinet TCP/IP software:
     $ SET DISPLAY/CREATE/NODE=nodename/TRANSPORT=TCPIP
If you have Wollengong TCP/IP software (WINTCP):
     $ SET DISPLAY/CREATE/NODE=nodename/TRANSPORT=WINTCP
